House Price Prediction

Subhasis Sur  MD2223

2022-11-06

Introduction

  • House is one of the most necessities in the human life.

  • A Good house is required for a good living.

  • For a Good House ,Cost of it is very important.

Objective

  • To Bulid a model for Predicting House Price.

  • Find relationships with some other things.

About Data

  • Source: Kaggle

  • Link of the Dataset: https://www.kaggle.com/code/burhanykiyakoglu/predicting-house-prices

  • This dataset contains house sale prices for King County, which includes Seattle, US.

  • 21613 rows (units of data) and 17 columns

Data Cleaning and Modification

  • Remove id, lat ,long coloumns

  • Extract only first 4 digits of zipcode

  • Convert yr_renovated to renovated

  • Convert renovated , zipcode ,grade ,condition , waterfront ,view , date into categorical variables.

  • Here, sqft living = sqft above + sqft basement

  • Remove sqft living coloumn

Relationship

  • A increasing relationship between grade and price

  • Little variation in price with the change in the condition of the house.

  • A increasing relationship between grade and sqft above

  • A increasing relationship between grade and sqft living15
